          "placeholder": "Luxury Chocolate Hamper | ₹3499 | A curated box of artisanal luxury chocolates. | /image1.jpg, Botanical Home Fragrance | ₹2899 | Hand-poured artisan candles. | /image2.jpg"
        }
      ]
    },
